research_municipality_step.notes: Garland, TX, operates under a council-manager system. Dylan Hedrick was elected Mayor in June 2025. The city council consists of eight members, each representing a district. Margaret Lucht also holds the role of Mayor Pro Tem, and Chris Ott holds the role of Deputy Mayor Pro Tem.
